Paste your Anthropic API key on a single line in a file named exactly:

    config/api_key.txt

(remove the ".example" suffix). Example contents:

sk-ant-api03-xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx

The key never leaves this machine — it is read only by the local app to call the
Claude API for notification assessments. Alternatively, set the environment
variable ANTHROPIC_API_KEY before launching (it takes precedence over this file).

Get a key at https://console.anthropic.com/
